This is Perl module App::pad.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - App::pad

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
App::pad:

    $ cpanm App::pad

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf App-pad-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd App-pad-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

App::pad documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc App::pad

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

